  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Safety and Efficacy of Ginsenoside Rg3 in Combination with First-line Chemotherapy in
      Advanced Gastric Cancer.The purpose of this study is to assess the safety of Ginsenoside Rg3
      in advanced gastric cancer, and whether it improves the efficacy of first-line chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
